On Debuffs...I just checked the spfdat and you are correct I don't see any different in resists of the spells listed. The only difference in malosi and malosini is that malosini lasts 1 min longer and takes 2 sec less to cast. So what is the advantage of casting it? They both debuff the same after level 50.<br>
